<div class="modal-header">
    <button type="button" {{action 'close'}} class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">Ã—</button>
    <h4 class="modal-title">{{course_name}}: Invite Students and Parents</h4>
</div>
<div class="modal-body">
    <form action="#" class="form-horizontal ">
        <div class="form-group">

            <div class="col-md-12">

                <h5>
                    In order for a parent or student to add <i>{{course_name}}</i> to WhatsDue, all they have to
                    do is enter this course code into the app: <strong>{{course_code}}</strong>
                </h5>
                <h5>
                    If you would like, we will send an email to whomever you wish, instructing them how to set up
                    WhatsDue and add this course.
                </h5>
                <h5>
                    The email will be sent from us, and <strong>your email address will be hidden</strong>
                </h5>
                <h5>
                    <strong><i>Note: The course code is automatically sent in the email.</i></strong>
                </h5>

                <h5>
                    Please feel free to change this text:
                </h5>
                {{textarea value=emailMessage class="form-control padded" placeholder="Message to your students"}}
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h5>
                    Please enter a list of email addresses. <i><strong>Recipients cannot see other email addresses</strong></i>
                </h5>
                {{textarea value=emailAddresses class="form-control padded" placeholder="List of emails seperated by commas, spaces, or new lines"}}
            </div>
        </div>

    </form>
</div>
<div class="modal-footer">
    <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" {{action 'send'}} >Send Email</button>
</div>